ZH: 请你来我家做客，我会招待你的。
EN: Please come to my house as a guest, I will entertain you.

ZH: 我们公司将为来访客户提供专业招待。
EN: Our company will provide professional hospitality to visiting clients.

ZH: 我们需要为宾客们准备一场盛大的招待会。
EN: We need to prepare a grand reception for the guests.

ZH: 他们以非常周到的招待而闻名。
EN: They are famous for their very thoughtful hospitality.

ZH: 我们将给参会者提供优质的招待。
EN: We will provide excellent hospitality for the participants.

ZH: 请务必招待好我们公司的合作伙伴。
EN: Please make sure to entertain our company's partners well.

ZH: 酒店的质量很好，服务人员给予我们极好的招待。
EN: The hotel has excellent quality, and the staff gave us excellent service.

ZH: 为了给客户留下深刻的印象，我们需要周到的招待。
EN: In order to leave a lasting impression on the clients, we need thoughtful hospitality.

ZH: 招待所在入口处的接待员会帮助您办理入住手续。
EN: The receptionist at the entrance of the guesthouse will assist you with check-in procedures.

ZH: 作为主人，我会尽力给我们的客人最好的招待。
EN: As the host, I will do my best to give our guests the best hospitality.

ZH: 我们需要在会议期间提供所有与会者的招待。
EN: We need to provide hospitality for all participants during the conference.

ZH: 她以热情招待来访的学者而闻名。
EN: She is famous for her warm hospitality towards visiting scholars.

ZH: 我们的顾客对我们的招待非常满意。
EN: Our customers are very satisfied with our hospitality.

ZH: 酒店设有一家优质的餐厅，为客人提供多样化的招待。
EN: The hotel has a high-quality restaurant that offers a variety of hospitality to guests.

ZH: 请务必确保给宾客提供周到的招待，以确保他们的满意度。
EN: Please make sure to provide thoughtful hospitality to guests to ensure their satisfaction.

ZH: 大使馆为重要嘉宾准备了一场隆重的招待宴会。
EN: The embassy has prepared a grand reception banquet for important guests.

ZH: 她总是给客人提供热情的招待和软性服务。
EN: She always offers guests warm hospitality and personalized services.

ZH: 作为主人，我们需要为客人提供尽可能好的招待。
EN: As hosts, we need to provide the best possible hospitality for our guests.

ZH: 我们的旅馆提供免费的早餐作为对客人的热情招待。
EN: Our hotel provides complimentary breakfast as a gesture of warm hospitality to guests.

ZH: 感谢您对我们的招待表示满意。
EN: Thank you for your satisfaction with our hospitality.
